<h2 class="header"><i>1</i>Thursday, January 31<a class="headerlink" href="#thursday-january-31" name="thursday-january-31">&para;</a></h2>
<p><a href="http://thales.math.uqam.ca/~tosun/Review-1.pdf">Questions</a></p>
<h3 class="header"><i>1.1</i>Question 1<a class="headerlink" href="#question-1" name="question-1">&para;</a></h3>
<ol>
<li>By rank-nullity</li>
<li>No, not necessarily</li>
</ol>
<h3 class="header"><i>1.2</i>Question 2<a class="headerlink" href="#question-2" name="question-2">&para;</a></h3>
<ol>
